  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2012-1508<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2012-11-22</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Whereas a Cree-Naskapi Commission was established by section 158 of the <em>Cree-Naskapi (of Quebec) Act</em>; \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Whereas it is necessary to appoint the members of the Commission and to designate the Chairman of the Commission; \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;And whereas the individual named herein has been recommended for appointment to the Commission by the Cree Regional Authority and the Naskapi Band of Quebec, as required by subsection 158(1) of the Act; \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Therefore, His Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development, pursuant to sections 158 and 160 of the <em>Cree-Naskapi (of Quebec) Act</em>:\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;(a)\t&nbsp;reappoints Robert Kanatewat of Chisasibi, Quebec, as a member of the Cree-Naskapi Commission for a term of two years;  \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;(b)\t&nbsp;fixes his remuneration at the per diem rate set out in the annexed schedule, which rate is within the range \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;($365 - $430); and  \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;(c)\t&nbsp;fixes his travel expenses in accordance with the rates and allowances set out in the National Joint Council Travel Directive and the Treasury Board Special Travel Authorities. \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Attendu qu’une Commission crie-naskapie a été établie en vertu de l’article 158 de la <em>Loi sur les Cris et les Naskapis du Québec</em>; \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Attendu qu’il est nécessaire de nommer les commissaires de cette Commission et d’en désigner le président; \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;Attendu que l’Administration régionale crie et la bande naskapie du Québec ont recommandé, tel que l’exige le paragraphe 158(1) de la loi, la nomination comme commissaire de la Commission, de la personne dont le nom figure ci-après, \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;À ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre des Affaires indiennes et du Nord canadien et en vertu des articles 158 et 160 de la <em>Loi sur les Cris et les Naskapis du Québec</em>, Son Excellence le Gouverneur général en conseil :\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;a)\t&nbsp;renouvelle le mandat de Robert Kanatewat, de Chisasibi (Québec), commissaire de la Commission crie-naskapie pour une période de deux ans;  \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;b)\t&nbsp;fixe sa rémunération selon le taux indiqué à l’annexe ci-jointe, lequel taux se situe dans l’échelle \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;\t&nbsp;(365 $ - 430 $) par jour; \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n\t&nbsp;c)\t&nbsp;fixe ses frais de déplacement conformément aux tarifs et indemnités de la directive sur les voyages du Conseil national mixte et les autorisations spéciales de voyager du Conseil du Trésor.  \n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;margin-right:2.00in;text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script typ